        <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://community.wildernesslabs.co/" class="nav-link px-2 text-muted">Community</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="https://blog.wildernesslabs.co/" class="nav-link px-2 text-muted">Blog</a></li>
